g.text: Scaling Out: Run Arcade on several hosts, add Geo/DNS or other load-balancer· Any number of VMs can serve a given game session. · Minio stores all persistent information in the system and handles replication between hosts.· Game sources may influence the PUBLIC RENDERER to customize the game VM build, as well as to implement game-play. · Individual nodejs server instances provide a gateway to Game Host and are otherwise disposable in-memory indexes into the minio.
